title: San Juan Island National Historical Park: Contact Public Affairs
body: Contact Public Affairs       For additional media inquiries, please contact the park's Public Information Officer, Doug Halsey, at: San Juan Island National Historical Park PO BOX 429 650 Mullis St., Suite 100 Friday Harbor, WA 98250 Phone: (360) 378-2240 x2228  Or you can send an e-mail by clicking here.
